1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 8 =

20
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:45,220
Your Majesty,

21
00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:49,860
Kong Daofu would like to talk with you.

22
00:01:50,980 --> 00:01:52,020
Please open the door.

23
00:01:53,260 --> 00:01:54,060
Your Majesty.

24
00:01:54,060 --> 00:01:56,500
Your Majesty, we think

25
00:01:56,700 --> 00:01:59,820
the Empress didn’t make any huge mistake,
so she shouldn’t be deposed.

26
00:02:00,260 --> 00:02:02,020
Please meet with us.

27
00:02:02,340 --> 00:02:04,900
Please meet with us.

28
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:07,700
- Open the door. - Your Majesty.

29
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:08,660
Open the door.

30
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:10,740
It’s burning hot out there.

31
00:02:11,060 --> 00:02:12,700
The imperial advisors

32
00:02:13,340 --> 00:02:15,020
are knocking at the door, yelling for a talk

33
00:02:15,540 --> 00:02:17,180
and have shouted themselves hoarse.

34
00:02:27,580 --> 00:02:29,380
It is not a nice thing

35
00:02:29,780 --> 00:02:31,420
to have advisors begging for a talk.

36
00:02:31,900 --> 00:02:33,540
Fan Zhongyan, Kong Daofu and others

37
00:02:33,540 --> 00:02:34,940
have gone against me repeatedly.

38
00:02:35,020 --> 00:02:36,940
This time they even disgraced themselves

39
00:02:36,980 --> 00:02:38,220
and the court.

40
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:40,260
They do not deserve to be
leading officials at the court.

41
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:43,580
Please evict Fan Zhongyan and
Kong Daofu out of the Capital.

42
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:45,180
But…

43
00:02:46,540 --> 00:02:47,740
Lv Yijian’s official letter.

44
00:02:50,860 --> 00:02:51,820
Is it about…

45
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:54,260
He complains about Guo

46
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:56,180
for saying he was a traitor too.

47
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:59,060
She said he stood with the Empress Dowager
and then fawned His Majesty

48
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:00,620
which shall be treated with revenge.

49
00:03:01,380 --> 00:03:02,340
But all he talks about

50
00:03:02,740 --> 00:03:05,220
is some empty about the country and the court.

51
00:03:05,980 --> 00:03:07,460
He doesn’t receive advisors’ advice,

52
00:03:07,620 --> 00:03:09,380
blocking the academy to draft the
announcement of deposing the Empress,

53
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:11,740
and letting them disgrace themselves

54
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:13,220
under the sun, knocking at the door.

55
00:03:13,220 --> 00:03:14,380
And then, he takes it as their sin.

56
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:16,980
He’s been treating advisors as fools

57
00:03:17,380 --> 00:03:18,780
and me as a kid.

58
00:03:21,780 --> 00:03:22,980
The Empress Dowager just deceased,

59
00:03:24,020 --> 00:03:25,940
both Yan Shu and Xia Song were demoted.

60
00:03:26,300 --> 00:03:27,220
If the Empress who hates him

61
00:03:27,220 --> 00:03:28,740
can be deposed,

62
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:31,700
Lv Yijian

63
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:34,180
would be a minister with great power.

64
00:03:35,060 --> 00:03:36,940
He has blocked the academy for
drafting the announcement…

65
00:03:40,540 --> 00:03:41,260
Your Majesty,

66
00:03:41,860 --> 00:03:42,900
should I

67
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:44,620
use some imperial guards?

68
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:47,660
What for?

69
00:03:48,780 --> 00:03:50,060
To besiege the Academy

70
00:03:50,380 --> 00:03:51,540
and take Lv Yijian down?

71
00:03:56,140 --> 00:03:56,860
It’s okay.

72
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,700
Although he insists on deposing the Empress

73
00:04:00,700 --> 00:04:01,740
out of selfish interest,

74
00:04:02,580 --> 00:04:04,220
Guo is indeed not qualified

75
00:04:04,900 --> 00:04:06,340
for her title.

76
00:04:09,180 --> 00:04:10,860
Before when we still had Her Majesty,

77
00:04:11,220 --> 00:04:12,900
I could just be tolerant

78
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:14,180
and hide from her.

79
00:04:14,900 --> 00:04:17,740
But now she’s responsible for managing the harem.

80
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:24,460
We didn’t wait for long to see
her causing a trouble.

81
00:04:24,540 --> 00:04:25,620
If we still keep her at her position,

82
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:27,620
what chaos will she create in the future?

83
00:04:30,220 --> 00:04:31,420
She does not match with her position.

84
00:04:32,140 --> 00:04:32,940
Keeping her

85
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:35,380
is not the mercy to her.

86
00:04:36,060 --> 00:04:37,060
Open the door!

87
00:04:37,780 --> 00:04:39,300
Please meet with us!

88
00:04:39,460 --> 00:04:41,100
- Please meet with us!- Open the door!

89
00:04:41,540 --> 00:04:44,980
Our proposals got rejected.

90
00:04:45,220 --> 00:04:47,180
Please meet with us!

91
00:04:47,900 --> 00:04:49,140
Open the door!

92
00:04:49,220 --> 00:04:52,100
- Your Majesty! -Only fatuous emperors
would depose their empresses.

93
00:04:52,420 --> 00:04:55,100
Your Majesty! You can’t depose the Empress!

94
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:57,100
You can’t!

95
00:04:57,260 --> 00:04:58,740
Your Majesty!

96
00:04:58,740 --> 00:04:59,449
Your Majesty!

97
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:00,980
Open the door!

98
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:03,220
You can’t follow

99
00:05:03,220 --> 00:05:04,780
what fatuous emperors do!

100
00:05:04,780 --> 00:05:07,060
- Only fatuous emperors would
depose their empresses. - Let go of me!

101
00:05:07,180 --> 00:05:08,860
Your Majesty! You can’t!

102
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:10,380
Only fatuous emperors would…

103
00:05:10,780 --> 00:05:12,260
I want to talk with His Majesty!

104
00:05:26,380 --> 00:05:29,260
Fan Zhongyan, Kong Daofu and the rest are bigoted.

105
00:05:30,340 --> 00:05:33,860
I’ve repeatedly sent people to tell them to leave.

106
00:05:34,220 --> 00:05:35,980
Yet still they insist

107
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:38,980
to stand at the gate

108
00:05:39,500 --> 00:05:41,420
saying disgraceful words

109
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:43,700
that humiliates themselves as officials.

110
00:05:44,180 --> 00:05:45,380
They must be punished.

111
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:51,940
Your Majesty,

112
00:05:52,580 --> 00:05:54,420
if they can’t

113
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:55,620
be punished,

114
00:05:56,260 --> 00:05:57,700
Once they started to

115
00:05:58,340 --> 00:06:00,100
force you

116
00:06:00,380 --> 00:06:02,620
in the name of loyalty…

117
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:03,500
Right,

118
00:06:05,020 --> 00:06:06,340
you made a point.

119
00:06:08,260 --> 00:06:09,260
But there’s another thing.

120
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:15,020
Li Di and the rest also made a good point.

121
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:20,740
Talking about disgrace,

122
00:06:20,820 --> 00:06:22,540
Shang and Yang made bigger mistakes.

123
00:06:22,900 --> 00:06:23,820
They seduced the Emperor,

124
00:06:23,900 --> 00:06:25,620
offended the Empress,

125
00:06:26,820 --> 00:06:28,020
and colluded with officials.

126
00:06:34,860 --> 00:06:36,260
Guo should be deposed for her moral demerit,

127
00:06:37,260 --> 00:06:38,700
but they should be punished too

128
00:06:39,340 --> 00:06:40,340
for offending the Empress.

129
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:48,260
Evict the three of them.

130
00:06:48,620 --> 00:06:50,700
As for their accommodations…

131
00:06:51,420 --> 00:06:53,660
Maoze, take care of it.

132
00:06:53,780 --> 00:06:54,740
Treat with discreetness.

133
00:06:55,940 --> 00:06:56,660
Yes, Your Majesty.

134
00:06:59,380 --> 00:07:01,780
Prime Minister Lv, anything else?

135
00:07:05,100 --> 00:07:06,020
I

136
00:07:07,340 --> 00:07:08,380
should leave now.

137
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:28,780
It is cool outside. Please go back.

138
00:07:36,020 --> 00:07:36,900
I can’t let

139
00:07:36,900 --> 00:07:38,900
the disqualified Guo to hold her position.

140
00:07:41,380 --> 00:07:44,700
Lv Yijian wants to build up his
reputation to control the court,

141
00:07:45,820 --> 00:07:48,100
while Fan Zhongyan is
determined to be a flawless man.

142
00:07:52,020 --> 00:07:53,140
After all these,

143
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:56,500
who will win the battle?

144
00:08:08,740 --> 00:08:10,620
Is Fan Xiwen in the carriage?

145
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:16,820
Mr. Ge?

146
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:22,620
I’m in Tonglu County now.

147
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:24,980
Mr. Fan.

148
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:30,580
After I heard that you were demoted to Mu State,

149
00:08:30,900 --> 00:08:32,300
= Ge Hong (Zirong) Zhang Min (Bozhen)
I feel sorry for you

150
00:08:32,620 --> 00:08:34,180
but excited to meet you again.

151
00:08:34,940 --> 00:08:35,900
I’ve prepared some good wine

152
00:08:35,980 --> 00:08:37,180
to wait for you.

153
00:08:43,060 --> 00:08:44,300
Tonglu deserves the reputation

154
00:08:44,300 --> 00:08:45,860
it enjoys for its magnificent scenery.

155
00:08:47,180 --> 00:08:48,740
I was demoted for giving my opinion,

156
00:08:48,740 --> 00:08:50,660
but His Majesty picked such a good place for me.

157
00:09:17,060 --> 00:09:19,220
Be careful, Mr. Fan!

158
00:09:29,060 --> 00:09:31,820
He is the only one

159
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:34,860
who can be so optimistic after being demoted.

160
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:38,100
Beautiful Tonglu

161
00:09:39,060 --> 00:09:40,740
is hidden in mountains and clouds.

162
00:09:42,380 --> 00:09:44,140
It frees all my troubles

163
00:09:44,900 --> 00:09:47,060
and empties my worries.

164
00:09:49,460 --> 00:09:50,860
Beautiful Tonglu

165
00:09:51,020 --> 00:09:52,820
impressed me at my first sight.

166
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:55,180
How blessed I am

167
00:09:55,860 --> 00:09:57,820
to be able to enjoy such a scenery every day.

168
00:10:05,900 --> 00:10:06,620
Your Majesty,

169
00:10:07,060 --> 00:10:08,100
about deposing the Empress,

170
00:10:08,660 --> 00:10:10,460
Your Majesty didn’t listened to advisors,

171
00:10:10,620 --> 00:10:13,460
and instead demoted Kong Daofu and Fan Zhongyan,

172
00:10:13,580 --> 00:10:15,900
punished Sun Zude and Song Xiang.

173
00:10:16,100 --> 00:10:18,020
Usually, when Imperial Minister is ousted,

174
00:10:18,220 --> 00:10:19,420
he would apply for it himself.

175
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:23,020
But this time, you dismissed him directly.

176
00:10:36,340 --> 00:10:39,100
I believe at a time in peace,

177
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:40,980
it is disgraceful for advisors

178
00:10:41,420 --> 00:10:45,260
to push and force His Majesty
by gathering at the gate.

179
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:46,660
= Gao Ruone, courtesy name Minzhi =
They should be ousted.

180
00:10:46,660 --> 00:10:47,900
It’s the most appropriate punishment for them.

181
00:10:48,540 --> 00:10:50,700
I think from now on,

182
00:10:51,020 --> 00:10:53,020
proposals from advisors

183
00:10:53,380 --> 00:10:54,980
should be sent to Your Majesty in confidentially.

184
00:10:55,500 --> 00:10:57,940
Prime Minister shouldn’t review them.

185
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:02,620
That’s ridiculous!

186
00:11:08,460 --> 00:11:09,780
From our first Emperor to the late Emperor,

187
00:11:10,060 --> 00:11:11,020
it’s been 70 years.

188
00:11:11,260 --> 00:11:12,820
We never had an empress deposed.

189
00:11:13,660 --> 00:11:15,300
But His Majesty didn’t abide
by the rules set by ancestors.

190
00:11:15,940 --> 00:11:17,420
If you don’t manage your family with rules,

191
00:11:17,420 --> 00:11:18,300
how can you manage the country?

192
00:11:18,940 --> 00:11:20,420
Fan Zhongyan, as an advisor,

193
00:11:20,620 --> 00:11:21,780
was just doing his job

194
00:11:21,940 --> 00:11:22,900
by trying to persuade Your Majesty.

195
00:11:23,460 --> 00:11:24,580
If what he proposed is not appropriate,

196
00:11:24,940 --> 00:11:26,140
Your Majesty should be tolerant

197
00:11:26,420 --> 00:11:27,740
to access more suggestions and opinions.

198
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:29,460
Besides, what Fan Zhongyan proposed

199
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:31,140
is what people want.

200
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:33,100
= Fu Bi, courtesy name Yanguo =
Why did Your Majesty punish him?

201
00:11:44,300 --> 00:11:45,860
Guo does not deserve her position

202
00:11:47,900 --> 00:11:48,940
and has been deposed.

203
00:11:49,340 --> 00:11:50,780
The vacancy should be filled before long.

204
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:54,820
Have you considered any candidates

205
00:11:55,100 --> 00:11:56,420
for this position?

206
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:01,340
Brilliant.

207
00:12:02,540 --> 00:12:05,700
It is the right thing to do

208
00:12:06,060 --> 00:12:07,220
to choose a qualified empress to lead the harem.

209
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:12,400
Recently,

210
00:12:12,820 --> 00:12:14,700
there are much less impeachment from advisors.

211
00:12:15,140 --> 00:12:17,260
They are all thinking
about the candidates for the Empress,

212
00:12:17,420 --> 00:12:18,940
and can’t spare their time on other things.

213
00:12:21,820 --> 00:12:23,620
It is indeed the biggest issue

214
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:25,100
we are concerned about now.

215
00:12:26,700 --> 00:12:28,940
When you mentioned to have a new empress soon,

216
00:12:29,700 --> 00:12:31,100
do you have anyone in mind?

217
00:12:34,740 --> 00:12:35,820
It’s never my decision

218
00:12:36,820 --> 00:12:38,540
on whom I marry.

219
00:12:40,700 --> 00:12:41,820
Before, it was the Empress Dowager

220
00:12:41,860 --> 00:12:43,620
choosing a daughter-in-law she could control,

221
00:12:43,940 --> 00:12:45,100
now it’s the vassals

222
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:48,300
choosing the mother of the whole
country the people want.

223
00:12:50,540 --> 00:12:51,980
I mentioned that

224
00:12:52,540 --> 00:12:54,620
because only by having a new empress

225
00:12:55,340 --> 00:12:56,980
can the tumult about the
empress deposition subside.

226
00:12:59,060 --> 00:13:00,300
I just deposed a

227
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:02,340
disqualified empress,

228
00:13:02,820 --> 00:13:05,420
but it gradually evolved into factional dispute.

229
00:13:12,734 --> 00:13:13,976
So cute!

230
00:13:14,620 --> 00:13:15,620
Xichun, Xichun!

231
00:13:18,540 --> 00:13:20,220
Xichun, Xichun, come on!

232
00:13:20,334 --> 00:13:21,060
Come on.

233
00:13:22,540 --> 00:13:23,380
Come here!

234
00:13:23,745 --> 00:13:24,780
Awesome!

235
00:13:24,780 --> 00:13:25,700
Why can it move?

236
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:28,500
Xichun, hurry up?

237
00:13:29,980 --> 00:13:30,780
How is it made?

238
00:13:30,900 --> 00:13:32,420
I copied the southward-pointing cart

239
00:13:32,620 --> 00:13:33,540
made by Mr. Yansu

240
00:13:33,540 --> 00:13:35,100
in the Fifth Year of Tiansheng.

241
00:13:36,100 --> 00:13:38,220
= Chen Xichun =
But mine is crude.

242
00:13:38,820 --> 00:13:39,900
His cart

243
00:13:40,020 --> 00:13:40,980
can run farther

244
00:13:41,020 --> 00:13:42,260
and avoid obstacles.

245
00:13:43,860 --> 00:13:45,380
-That’s awesome! - That’s awesome!

246
00:13:45,660 --> 00:13:46,220
Xichun,

247
00:13:46,300 --> 00:13:47,020
how can the cart

248
00:13:47,020 --> 00:13:48,100
move by itself?

249
00:13:48,220 --> 00:13:49,180
Yeah.

250
00:13:50,220 --> 00:13:50,900
Why can it move

251
00:13:50,900 --> 00:13:52,180
towards the one direction?

252
00:13:52,291 --> 00:13:53,477
Why?

253
00:13:56,420 --> 00:13:57,060
It’s in here.

254
00:13:57,220 --> 00:13:57,980
Look,

255
00:13:58,140 --> 00:13:59,260
there are different gear wheels.

256
00:13:59,260 --> 00:14:00,100
So many?

257
00:14:01,420 --> 00:14:02,820
Can you teach us?

258
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,767
Yeah, tell us.

259
00:14:08,020 --> 00:14:08,860
Maoze.

260
00:14:11,980 --> 00:14:12,700
Your Majesty.

261
00:14:14,460 --> 00:14:15,700
Which Palace are they from?

262
00:14:15,708 --> 00:14:20,800
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

263
00:14:20,818 --> 00:14:23,900
= Hall of Happiness and Tranquility =

264
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:42,980
Your Majesty, Ms. Chen Xichun is here.

265
00:14:48,740 --> 00:14:49,580
Your Majesty.

266
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:53,100
Chen Xichun (enchanting spring).

267
00:14:54,820 --> 00:14:57,340
Chill autumn ends the summer heat,
enchanting spring ends the winter coldness.

268
00:14:57,900 --> 00:14:59,940
You were born in the early spring?

269
00:15:00,500 --> 00:15:01,180
Yes.

270
00:15:02,020 --> 00:15:03,420
I was born in early March,

271
00:15:03,740 --> 00:15:04,740
and just turned 16.

272
00:15:07,540 --> 00:15:09,060
You are from Consort Yang’s Palace.

273
00:15:09,140 --> 00:15:11,300
I never saw you before.

274
00:15:12,340 --> 00:15:14,100
I’ve only been here for less than a month.

275
00:15:14,380 --> 00:15:15,940
Consort Yang took me as her adoptive daughter.

276
00:15:17,740 --> 00:15:18,900
You came into the Palace

277
00:15:18,900 --> 00:15:20,180
